main event: A sound object was sighted near San Antonio International Airport on 5 August 1965, observed for about 3 minutes.
interesting points: The object was initially noted due to an observed sound., The observer described a flash of light and a jittering appearance of the object., The observer thought the object followed a T-38 aircraft., Heavy airport traffic was present during the sighting., During interviews, potential explanations for the sounds included an emergency vehicle or construction equipment noise.
